line_1: But give him Port, and potent Sack;
line_2: From Milk-sop He starts up Moback:

line_1: A sturdy Collier prest the empty sack,
line_2: A troop of thousands swarming on his back;

line_1: Thy carcase is sound as a sack,
The mighty monarch, in theatric sack,
line_2: Carries his whole regalia at his back;
